<C>__{officer}
<D>__{they don't look like you.}
<C>__{amelia}
<P>__{(bewildered)}
<D>__{i'm in charge of them.}
<C>__{officer}
<D>__{do you have their passports?}
<A>__{amelia takes out their american passports and shows them to the cop. he looks them over very carefully. santiago starts to get nervous.}
<C>__{santiago}
